41:41.958 --> 41:43.949
But it's not just work.

41:45.128 --> 41:47.835
Why raise your kids
when a dolly can do it?

41:48.715 --> 41:51.331
Why cook your family a meal
when a dolly can do it?

41:51.467 --> 41:53.128
Why go on a date?

41:53.261 --> 41:55.217
Why try to get to know someone

41:55.346 --> 41:57.177
when you can pay a dolly
for sex?

41:57.306 --> 42:01.174
In every area of human life,
they are coming between us.

42:01.310 --> 42:04.802
We don't know how to connect
to each other, only to them.

42:04.939 --> 42:08.978
And now we can't even trust them
not to hurt us.

42:09.986 --> 42:12.068
We are stumbling
towards the precipice.

42:12.196 --> 42:14.653
We're racing towards it
willingly,

42:14.782 --> 42:17.945
with a smile on our face
and a dolly's hand in ours!

42:18.077 --> 42:19.942
Yes, we are people!

42:20.079 --> 42:23.037
We are people!
We are people!

42:23.166 --> 42:25.999
ALL: We are people!
We are people!

42:26.127 --> 42:28.038
We are people!

42:30.506 --> 42:32.167
Did you speak to Tobe?

42:35.636 --> 42:37.217
It, um...

42:39.348 --> 42:40.724
It wasn't him.

42:48.066 --> 42:49.181
Uh...

42:50.818 --> 42:52.854
I'd had a few glasses of wine.

42:55.406 --> 42:57.237
I was pissed off with you.

42:58.493 --> 43:01.485
